com.camerontec.catalys.server.adapter.solace

Class SolaceStringFIXSendingTransformer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.server.adapter.TechnologyAdapterFIXSendingTransformer
      • com.camerontec.catalys.server.adapter.solace.SolaceStringFIXSendingTransformer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IFromMessageTransformer, IMessageTransformer, IToMessageTransformer, ISolaceMessageTransformer

    public class SolaceStringFIXSendingTransformer
extends TechnologyAdapterFIXSendingTransformer
implements ISolaceMessageTransformer
    IMessageTransformer implementation for transforming messages between Catalys and Solace where each Solace message is a TextMessage whose payload is a String.

    This transformer ensures that the outbound FIX payload contains properly ordered tags and a valid BodyLength and CheckSum.

    Each instance of this class will have its own buffers. And since SolaceMessageSource and SolaceMessageListener instances are bound to their respective sessions, buffer contents will not be shared between sessions (FSD-66869).
